http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/title.value: Providing Real Opportunities for Vocational Education

http://purl.org/dc/terms/description.value: Providing Real Opportunities for Vocational Education is a program of instruction based on identified student needs in regard to the improvement of vocational and academic scores and/or skills while utilizing a versatile spectrum of instruction.
